  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK966">
<l>pukaḻiṉṟāṟ puttēṇāṭ ṭuyyātā leṉmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟikaḻvārpiṉ ceṉṟu nilai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of what good is it (for the high-born) to go and stand in vain before those who revile him ? it only brings him loss of honour and exclusion from heaven.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
